[SN]TITLE[SN]
Rio Olympics 2016: Argentina beat Belgium 4-2 in the men's hockey final

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Argentina won Olympic men's hockey gold for the first time with a 4-2 victory over Belgium in Rio.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
